      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if i take 400mg every 2 hours, thats only 1200mg in 6 hours. if i keep doing that for the rest of the day, wouldnt it just stay at a steady level in my blood so the pain never spikes? the 1200mg limit seems pretty low if the pain is actually constant.",
