      "content": "i get the risks, but i really cant afford to go to a doctor right now and the pain is just too much. if i'm careful and just take it every 2 hours like i said, won't i be fine? it's just a temporary thing for a couple of days while my back heals. it seems like a much better way to handle it than just suffering through the spikes.",
